July 2008 - Bukhari went to The Sports Bar [a café in the Tauheed Commercial Area of Karach] in a black BMW, license plate KAB 8407, at 1145. He and another man, possibly Akram Basra (a known associate of Bukhari) entered TSB, both then proceeded to a private meeting room and stayed for 75 minutes. Bukhari exited the café with Basra about 1300, where the same BMW was waiting to pick them up. The automobile left, heading west.
